title: 18. Freakonomics FAQ, No. 1
description: Levitt and Dubner field questions from the public and hold forth on everything from dating strategies and rock-and-roll accordion music to whether different nations have different economic identities. Oh, and also: is it worthwhile to vote?
author: editor@freakonomics.com (Freakonomics Radio + Stitcher)
